{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"06321ba3d9","title":"给自己诗词作的解释","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[],"tags":[{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui4","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1958-1960卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui4a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui4":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"09ba70f7fb","type":"title","text":"给自己诗词作的解释","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"210a087dfa","type":"paragraph","text":"我的几首词发表后，注家蜂起，全是好心。一部分说对了，一部分说的不对。我有说明的责任。一九五八年在广州，见一九五八年刊本，天头甚宽，因而，写了下面一些字，谢注家兼谢读者。鲁迅在一九二七年在广州修改他的《古小说钩沉》后记中说道：“于时云海沉沉，星月澄碧餮蚊逞强，于在广州。”从那时到今天，三十一年了，大陆上的蚊灭得差不多了。当然革命尚未全成，同志们仍需努力。港台一带，餮蚊尚多，西方世界，餮蚊成阵。安得其全世界各民族千百万愚公，用他们自己的移山办法，把蚊阵一扫而空，岂不伟哉！","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"162024bba7","type":"paragraph","text":"试仿陆放翁曰：","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0f8ba14360","type":"paragraph","text":"人类今天上太空，但悲不见五洲同。愚公尽扫餮蚊日，公祭毋忘告马翁。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"be0a1981cb","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东一九五八年十二月二十一日上午十时","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6b7fbde80e","type":"paragraph","text":"沁园春.长沙","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fb48c4e19c","type":"subdate","text":"一九二五年","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1ddc9cfa0f","type":"paragraph","text":"击水：（到中流击水，浪遏飞舟）","index":7,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c91d0de84f","type":"paragraph","text":"游泳，那时初学，盛夏水涨，几死者数。一群入终于坚持到隆冬。犹在水中。当时有一篇忘记了。只记得两句：“自信人生两百年，会当击水三千里。”","index":8,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f3c194cb8b","type":"paragraph","text":"菩萨蛮.黄鹤楼","index":9,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2c03795432","type":"subdate","text":"一九二七年","index":10,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8fe0278ae2","type":"paragraph","text":"心潮：（把酒酌滔滔。心潮逐浪高）","index":11,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8d5efc64bd","type":"paragraph","text":"一九二七年大革命失败的前夕，心情苍凉，一时不知如何是好。这是那年春季。夏季八月七日，党的紧急会议决定武装斗争。从此才找到了出路。","index":12,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"787c3faf96","type":"paragraph","text":"清平乐.会昌","index":13,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"028c06e6af","type":"paragraph","text":"一九三四年夏","index":14,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b1215d3c1d","type":"paragraph","text":"踏遍青山人未老：（踏遍青山人未老，风景这边独好。）","index":15,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1ccd490286","type":"paragraph","text":"一九三四年形势危急。准备长征，心情又是郁闷的。这首清平乐与前面那首菩萨蛮一样，表露了同一的心情。","index":16,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"78bfd58ce8","type":"paragraph","text":"忆泰娥.娄山关","index":17,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"58dcbb7548","type":"subdate","text":"一九三五年","index":18,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"48f34ee39c","type":"paragraph","text":"万里长征，千回百折。胜少于困难不知多少倍。心情是沉郁的。过了岷山，豁然开朗，转到了反面，柳暗花明又一村了。以下几首反映了这种心情。","index":19,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4d282ee29f","type":"paragraph","text":"七律.长征一九三五年十月","index":20,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"efb268e052","type":"paragraph","text":"水拍：（金沙水拍云崖暖，大渡桥横铁索寒）","index":21,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9c0532ed8b","type":"paragraph","text":"改水拍，这是一位不相识的朋友建议的。他说：不要一篇有两个“浪”字，是可以的。","index":22,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b754340ca7","type":"paragraph","text":"三军：（更喜岷山千里雪，三军过后尽开颜。）","index":23,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c494e40f31","type":"paragraph","text":"红军一方面军、二方面军、四方面军。不是陆海空三军，也不是古代晋国所谓上军，中军、下军的三军。","index":24,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"14d66b9386","type":"paragraph","text":"念奴娇.昆仑","index":25,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cc40173ac2","type":"subdate","text":"一九三五年十月","index":26,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e0b03775c4","type":"paragraph","text":"主题思想是反对帝国主义，不是别的。后一句：“一截留中国”改为“一截还东国”。忘记了日本人民是不对的。这样，英、美、日都涉及了。别的解释不合实际。","index":27,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"22f6f1a62a","type":"paragraph","text":"清平乐.六盘山","index":28,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ec81900a76","type":"subdate","text":"一九三五年十月","index":29,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2bcb645a65","type":"paragraph","text":"苍龙：（今日长缨在手，何时缚住苍龙？）指蒋介石。不是日本人。因为当时全付精力要对付的是蒋不是日。","index":30,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9df0a323c1","type":"paragraph","text":"沁园春.雪","index":31,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6ad7ed176e","type":"subdate","text":"一九三六年二月","index":32,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1d8d70b203","type":"paragraph","text":"反对封建主义，批判两千年来的封建主义的一个反动侧面。","index":33,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"509dbd9ea8","type":"paragraph","text":"文釆、风骚、大雕，只能如此，须知这是写诗啊，难道可以咒骂这些人吗？别的解释是错误的。","index":34,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"02dad1fdd9","type":"paragraph","text":"末三句，指无产阶级。","index":35,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"03b729d4a1","type":"paragraph","text":"七律.和柳亚子先生","index":36,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ca48905dbb","type":"subdate","text":"一九四九年四月二十九日","index":37,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b5db366169","type":"paragraph","text":"三十一年：（三十一年还旧国。落花时节馈华章）","index":38,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9a5be1dbf0","type":"paragraph","text":"一九一九年离开北京。一九四九年还北京。旧国之国：都城。不是Ltoho（国家）。也不是 Country（首都）。","index":39,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a1eecd3d37","type":"paragraph","text":"浣溪纱.和柳亚子先生","index":40,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d69842d9ee","type":"subdate","text":"一九五○年十月","index":41,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e0294ca57a","type":"paragraph","text":"乐奏：（万方乐奏有于阗）这里误置为“奏乐”。应改。（现版已改）","index":42,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1a13e8abf0","type":"paragraph","text":"水调歌头.游泳","index":43,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e9c4938a77","type":"subdate","text":"一九五六年六月","index":44,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9422bb2655","type":"paragraph","text":"长沙水：（才饮长沙水）民谣：“常德山山有德，长沙水水无沙”。所谓长沙水，在常德东。有一个有名的“白沙井”。","index":45,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ea62d1d432","type":"paragraph","text":"武昌鱼：（又食武昌鱼）","index":46,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d4010f39a7","type":"paragraph","text":"三国孙权一度从京口（镇江）迁都武昌。官僚、绅士、地主及富裕阶层不悦，反对迁都。造出口号云：“宁饮扬州（建业）水。不食武昌鱼”。那时的扬州人，心情如此。现在改变了。武昌鱼是颇有味道的。","index":47,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"06321ba3d9","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":365,"end":362}}}},"__N_SSG":true}